"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0201.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0177","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0177.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0200","title":"Microsoft Clip Art Gallery 5.0 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Microsoft Clip Art Gallery 5.0 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向受害者发送特制的 CIL（剪贴画库）文件触发该漏洞，导致目标系统拒绝服务或执行任意命令。该漏洞源于程序在处理畸形 CIL 文件时未正确校验输入长度，造成缓冲区越界写入。攻击者需诱使用户打开恶意 CIL 文件才能成功利用，CVSS 评分 5.1，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0200"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-03-06T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:12.620","remediation":"安装微软安全公告 MS00-017 提供的更新补丁。由于 Microsoft Clip Art Gallery 5.0 属于 Office 2000 组件且已停止技术支持，建议升级到受支持的 Microsoft Office 版本（Office 2016 及以上），或在组策略中禁用 Clip Art Gallery 组件，避免打开来源不明的 .cil 剪贴画库文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1034","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-015","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19789","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad08212eac84f46206c2da8a50436d48e5ad608c/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0200.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0200","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0200.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/baa4573f2fa6813cfbc3f5cda2f1796a92d64bdf/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0200.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/95e6ff620d5494b93ba2234edfcf6a45187dc0a8/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-36fv-7fxv-xr4g/GHSA-36fv-7fxv-xr4g.json","https://github.com/CERTCC/SBOM/blob/ae581e32992458f65018df4eced684b7370bba39/SwiftBOM/cpe_lookup/cve_lookup/microsoft/greetings_cve.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0200.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152200_152300.json","https://github.com/akabe1/windows_exploit_dowser/blob/11b24e36173cd382721db28581e575faf687d06b/cve_from_exploitdb_website.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0177.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0182","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0182.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0206","title":"Oracle8i Standard Edition 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Oracle 8.1.5.x for Linux 安装程序在安装过程中会跟随符号链接，并以全局可写权限创建 orainstRoot.sh 脚本文件，导致本地用户可通过创建指向关键系统文件的符号链接，诱导安装程序覆盖关键文件从而实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 Oracle8i Standard Edition 8.1.5 for Linux 版本，攻击者需具备本地用户权限且能创建符号链接，利用方式为预先创建指向敏感文件（如 /etc/passwd 或 /etc/sudoers）的符号链接，待 Oracle 安装程序运行时跟随链接并以世界可写权限创建或覆盖目标文件，导致权限提升。CVSS 评分 6.2，属于本地权限提升漏洞，Oracle 已在后续版本中修复该符号链接跟随及权限设置缺陷。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0206"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-03-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:13.403","remediation":"建议升级至 Oracle8i 8.1.6 或更高版本，该版本修复了安装程序跟随符号链接并创建全局可写 orainstRoot.sh 的问题。若无法立即升级，可在安装前手动创建 orainstRoot.sh 并设置权限为 755，或限制普通用户对 Oracle 安装目录的写入权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-03/0023.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1035","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19794","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad08212eac84f46206c2da8a50436d48e5ad608c/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0206.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0206","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0206.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/72b66ad516fae