plates/advisory.html?id=2126","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=NCBBKFKDOLAGKIAPMILPCENECCAA.labs%40ussrback.com"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0148.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0148.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0148.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0181","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0181.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0205","title":"趋势科技 OfficeScan 远程配置篡改漏洞","description":"Trend Micro OfficeScan 存在远程管理命令重放漏洞，远程攻击者可通过网络嗅探捕获管理员与 OfficeScan 服务器之间未加密的通信流量，重放已捕获的管理命令，从而修改 OfficeScan 客户端的配置策略，导致客户端防护功能失效或服务中断。该漏洞影响 Trend Micro OfficeScan 早期版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可实施攻击，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0205"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-03-03T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:13.267","remediation":"立即升级 Trend Micro OfficeScan 至受支持的最新版本（Apex One 或 Worry-Free Business Security Services），该漏洞在后续版本中已修复。如无法升级，在管理控制台启用 HTTPS 通信和客户端身份验证，限制管理端口的网络访问来源，仅允许受信任的管理员 IP 连接，防止攻击者重放管理命令篡改客户端配置。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-03/0015.html","http://www.antivirus.com/download/ofce_patch_35.htm","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1013","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=D129BBE1730AD2118A0300805FC1C2FE038AF28B%40209-76-212-10.trendmicro.com","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/aa3114da1227373bef7855dba21bcaa5f0e0ad76/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0205.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0205","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0205.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/b4ddb28f94d250449ab64c1617f45b1f