ssenger 至 4.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，建议禁用 AIM 的消息预览功能或使用防火墙规则阻止来自不可信来源的即时消息连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-03/0016.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a662dc905cd549a2105daacbfce64cf01652761d/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0190.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0190","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0190.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cdbbe57bd34c799f670485304ef54912650bf03b/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0190.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-72ww-f3xx-777g/GHSA-72ww-f3xx-777g.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0190.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152200_152300.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001212.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d1651913-d3fe-461f-8de6-ddda583663c9.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/542ccf7ca1980a320a4dc1c4f0821b498d3bc23b/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0167.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0170","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0170.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0193","title":"Corel Linux 1.0 Dosemu 默认配置本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Corel Linux 1.0 中 Dosemu（DOS 模拟器）的默认配置存在安全缺陷，允许本地用户通过执行 system.com 程序获取系统最高权限。攻击者只需拥有本地访问权限，无需认证即可利用此漏洞完全控制系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0193"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"2000-03-02","updated":"2000-03-02","remediation":"限制 Dosemu 配置文件的访问权限，移除不必要的 setuid 权限设置，或升级到已修复此问题的 Corel Linux 更新版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T05:42:43.607542929+00:00","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1030","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=200003020436.PAA20168%40jawa.chilli.net.au"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0170.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0178","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0178.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0201","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 5.x 的 window.showHelp() 方法未正确限制 HTML 帮助文件（.chm）的执行来源，远程攻击者可通过 Microsoft Networking 协议诱导用户访问恶意网页，从而在本地执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Internet Explorer 5.x 系列版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，危害较大。微软已发布安全公告并提供修复补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0201"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:12.747","remediation":"立即停止使用 Internet Explorer 5.x，升级至 Internet Explorer 6 或更高版本（该漏洞在 IE 6 中已修复）。如无法升级，可通过注册表禁用 showHelp 功能：将 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\Main\\FeatureControl\\FEATURE_RESTRICT_ABOUT_PROTOCOL_IE7 设为 1。长期建议迁移至 Microsoft Edge 等现代浏览器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1033","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8de487bef2c8b1936da1237463dc6052a1fcd655/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0201.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0201","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0201.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/b4ddb28f94d250449ab64c1617f45b1f91701fa2/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0201.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-489p-9hgq-jg94/GHSA-489p-9hgq-jg94.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0201.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152200_152300.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--2c2e5f6f-3a39-42df-928a-348b2f4bc4b3.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/112b6cf2eb30218e492a77c7d1bcb2220cd940b5/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0178.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0178.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0166","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0166.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0189","title":"Allaire ColdFusion 远程服务器信息泄露漏洞","description":"Allaire ColdFusion Server 4.x 存在服务器信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求访问 application.cfm 或 onrequestend.cfm 文件，从而获取服务器的真实物理路径信息。该漏洞可被利用于进一步探测目标系统结构，为后续攻击提供信息支撑，影响运行 ColdFusion Server 4.x 的所有版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0189"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:11.173","remediation":"升级至 ColdFusion 5.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，在 Web 服务器（IIS/Apache）层面配置规则，拒绝外部对 `application.cfm` 和 `onrequestend.cfm` 文件的直接 HTTP 访问请求，仅允许 ColdFusion 引擎内部调用。同时禁用目录浏览功能，防止路径信息进一步泄露。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1021","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a662dc905cd549a2105daacbfce64cf01652761d/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0189.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0189","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0189.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cdbbe57bd34c799f670485304ef54912650bf03b/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0189.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4rjq-mf8f-5v58/GHSA-4rjq-mf8f-5v58.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0189.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152200_152300.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001207.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--2777226d-5035-4a7f-bf4e-606245495156.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0166.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0166.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0668","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0668.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0207","title":"SGI InfoSearch CGI 程序 infosrch.cgi 远程命令注入漏洞","description":"SGI InfoSearch 1.0 版本中的 infosrch.cgi CGI 程序存在命令注入漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向该 CGI 程序传入包含 shell 元字符的参数，在服务器端执行任意操作系统命令。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.5.x 系统，由于程序未对用户输入进行充分的过滤和转义处理，攻击者可利用此漏洞完全控制受影响的服务器，造成严重的信息泄露和系统沦陷风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0207"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"2000-03-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"应用 SGI 安全公告 20000501-01-P 提供的官方补丁，或直接禁用 InfoSearch CGI 程序 infosrch.cgi 的访问权限。若业务无需使用 InfoSearch 功能，建议从 Web 服务器配置中移除该 CGI 程序映射，并升级至 IRIX 后续安全更新版本以消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T06:46:40Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2000-0207","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1031"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0668.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0608","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0608.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0191","title":"Axis Communications StorPoint CD 身份认证绕过漏洞","description":"Axis Communications StorPoint CD 设备存在路径遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过在 URL 中注入 `..`（点点）序列绕过访问控制，直接访问管理员管理界面及敏感配置页面。该漏洞影响 StorPoint CD 系列设备，攻击者可利用此漏洞获取设备完全控制权限，进而篡改配置或窃取敏感信息。CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0191"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-02-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:11.463","remediation":"立即升级 Axis StorPoint CD 固件至厂商提供的最新版本。如设备已停止支持，应将管理界面绑定到内网特定 IP 或 VLAN，在防火墙上限制对设备 80/443 端口的访问来源，仅允许受信任管理 IP 连接。同时禁用不必要的 Web 管理功能，并在反向代理层过滤路径遍历特征（如 `..`、`%2e%2e`）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/19","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1025","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=41256894.00492503.00%40mailgw.backupcentralen.se","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19784","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1d6385d398a2a41185d3cc14943c25f73c724ba3/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0191.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0191","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/8854c056beab250ba690e2bcc8887feb4c1f8139/2000/CVE-2000-0191/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0191.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/baa4573f2fa6813cfbc3f5cda2f1796a92d64bdf/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0191.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/95e6ff620d5494b93ba2234edfcf6a45187dc0a8/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qxm8-579x-6fj9/GHSA-qxm8-579x-6fj9.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/A/axis.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_400_500.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0191.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0608.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0608.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0608.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0183","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0183.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0208","title":"ht://Dig Group ht://Dig htsearch 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"ht://Dig 是一款用于网站全文检索的开源搜索引擎。其 CGI 程序 htsearch 在处理请求参数时存在安全缺陷，远程攻击者可在传递给 htsearch 的参数中使用反引号（`）包裹文件名，从而触发任意文件读取。受影响版本包括 ht://Dig 3.1.1 至 3.1.4 以及 3.2.0b1。攻击者无需身份认证，只需向存在漏洞的 htsearch 接口发送特制参数即可读取服务器上的任意文件，可能导致敏感配置、密码等关键信息泄露。该漏洞 CVSS 评分约 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0208"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-02-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:13.673","remediation":"立即将 ht://Dig 升级到 3.1.5 及以后修复版本，或升级到已修补的 3.2 正式版及以上，并替换所有 htsearch CGI。若无法马上升级，从 Web 服务器配置中移除或禁用 htsearch（如删除/重命名 cgi-bin 下的 htsearch 可执行文件），仅允许受信内网访问搜索接口，并在 Web/WAF 层过滤请求参数中的反引号（`）等 shell 元字符作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1026","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19785","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad13a04165adf44a190b93c89d746f49525e5595/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0208.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0208","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0208.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/72b66ad516faec962399c4214c080517aebc4c11/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0208.json","https://github.com/swimlane/soc-faker/blob/361c4ae88956878fbd8aaf5975044328556dfecd/socfaker/data/alert_names.txt","https://github.com/decal/werdlists/blob/81edb463f7f6311c85defefaf75ac9cd58e5cfb9/exploit-info/symantec-attack-signatures.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/h/htdig.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0208.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0183.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0191","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0191.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0216","title":"Microsoft Outlook、Exchange、Windows Messaging 电子邮件回执响应拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Outlook、Exchange 及 Windows Messaging 等电子邮件客户端默认自动处理邮件中的已读回执和送达回执标签。远程攻击者可伪造包含回执请求的邮件，将回执目标地址指向大型邮件列表，触发大量自动响应邮件，导致目标邮件系统被洪水消息淹没，造成拒绝服务。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0216"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-29","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 2000 年 3 月发布的安全更新 MS00-008，或在 Outlook 中取消勾选工具→选项→电子邮件选项→跟踪选项中的处理回执和送达回执选项，并在 Exchange 服务器上禁用自动回执响应功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/ntbugtraq/2000-q1/0176.html","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2000-0216"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0191.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0155","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0155.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0176","title":"Serv-U FTP 服务器路径泄漏漏洞","description":"Serv-U FTP 服务器 2.5d 及更早版本的默认配置存在路径泄漏漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过请求一个不存在的目录或文件 URL，即可从服务器返回的错误信息中获取服务器真实路径名。该漏洞可被用于信息收集，为后续攻击提供目标系统目录结构信息，影响范围较广，攻击复杂度低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0176"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-29","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Serv-U FTP 服务器至 2.5e 或更高版本，该版本修复了默认配置下错误信息泄露真实路径的问题。如无法升级，可修改服务器配置，禁用详细错误信息显示，避免向客户端返回真实路径名。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-02/0417.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1016"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0155.toml"}]